    'Review the passage and eliminate choices that contradict the text.',
    'The author’s use of rhetorical questions in the passage helps to make the argument seem more conversational and personal.  The author uses these questions as a way to engage the reader and to invite the reader to think critically about the topic at hand.  What is the best way to describe the function of the rhetorical questions?',
